  <prompt>Create `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Infrastructure/DI/CacheModuleTests.cs` with at least 4 test methods covering CacheModule's 4 branches (Redis-on, Redis-off-AllowFallback-Dev, Redis-off-AllowFallback-non-Dev throws, Redis-off-NoFallback throws), plus tests for NullConnectionMultiplexer (Subscribe = no-op, Publish returns 0, GetDatabase throws NotSupportedException). FR-08 + NFR-13.</prompt>
  <role>Spaarke .NET developer with xUnit/Moq familiarity. Use xUnit `[Fact]` style consistent with other unit tests in the project.</role>
  <goal>Test class `CacheModuleTests` with ≥6 test methods. All pass via `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/`. Tests are deterministic (no actual Redis dependency — Redis-on path mocks `IConnectionMultiplexer.Connect`).</goal>
  <context>
